{
  "texts": [
    "We recognize the importance of AI safety settings, especially when it comes to incredibly large models like Gemini.",
    "However, translation and chat are not equivalent tasks.",
    "Google is actively encouraging the use and deployment of Gemini in translation, evident in their report (Team, 2024) and in their investment in developing the MTOB benchmark (Tanzer et al., 2024).",
    "Translation is a standard use case in their basic usage examples.",
    "Yet, the company does not offer any details about how they see their safety settings interacting with translation."
  ]
}